### Steam Price Map API - Validation Tests
### This file contains examples of valid and invalid requests to test input validation

### VALID REQUESTS ###

### Valid request - Get game info with EUR currency
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/730?currency=EUR
Accept: application/json

###

### Valid request - Get game info with USD currency
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/730?currency=USD
Accept: application/json

###

### Valid request - Search for games
GET https://localhost:5001/api/GameSearch/searchGame?search=Counter-Strike
Accept: application/json

###

### Valid request - Get engine status
GET https://localhost:5001/api/Engine/status
Accept: application/json

###

### INVALID REQUESTS - Testing Validation ###

### Invalid AppId - Zero
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/0?currency=EUR
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid AppId - Negative
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/-1?currency=EUR
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid Currency - Too short
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/730?currency=EU
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid Currency - Too long
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/730?currency=EURO
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid Currency - Lowercase
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/730?currency=eur
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid Currency - Numbers
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/730?currency=123
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid Currency - Special characters
GET https://localhost:5001/api/PriceMap/game/730?currency=E$R
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid Search - Empty string (will return empty results, not error)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/GameSearch/searchGame?search=
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid Search - Too long (over 200 characters)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/GameSearch/searchGame?search=ThisIsAVeryLongSearchTermThatExceedsTwoHundredCharactersWhichIsTheMaximumAllowedLengthForSearchQueriesInThisAPIThisIsDesignedToTestTheValidationLogicAndEnsureThatItProperlyRejectsSearchTermsThatAreTooLongAndPreventsAnyPotentialIssuesWithDatabaseOrPerformance
Accept: application/json

###

